INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2020-01-17 16:52:35','2020-01-17 16:52:35','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start writing!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2020-01-17 16:52:35','2020-01-17 16:52:35','',0,'http://doctorsconnect.test/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2020-01-17 16:52:35','2020-01-17 16:52:35','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>...or something like this:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p></blockquote>\n<!-- /wp:quote -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Sample Page','','publish','closed','open','','sample-page','','','2020-01-17 16:52:35','2020-01-17 16:52:35','',0,'http://doctorsconnect.test/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(3,1,'2020-01-17 16:52:35','2020-01-17 16:52:35','<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n</p>\n<h2>Who we are</h2>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>Our website address is: http://doctorsconnect.test.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n</p>\n<h2>What personal data we collect and why we collect it</h2>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n</p>\n<h3>Comments</h3>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor’s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n</p>\n<h3>Media</h3>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n</p>\n<h3>Contact forms</h3>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n</p>\n<h3>Cookies</h3>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select \"Remember Me\", your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n</p>\n<h3>Embedded content from other websites</h3>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n</p>\n<p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.</p>\n<p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<p></p>','Privacy Policy','','publish','closed','open','','privacy-policy','','','2020-01-26 14:23:34','2020-01-26 14:23:34','',0,'http://doctorsconnect.test/?page_id=3',0,'page','',0),(6,1,'2020-01-17 18:58:42','2020-01-17 18:58:42','<h1>ABOUT US<br></h1>		\n			<h2>Aim and Vision</h2>		\n		<p><strong>Doctors Connect Foundation Malaysia</strong>’s sole aim is in creating access for quality healthcare to remote inaccessible and poor socio-economic areas to provide quality medical screening and care for the needy and unfortunate irrespective of race, religion or nationality – all <strong>FREE</strong> of cost!</p>\n<p><br></p><p>Our vision is unity in diversity - breaking boundaries of race religion and nationality and seeing one in all. Our mission is to provide free, high quality, and compassionate medical care to the underprivileged communities in Malaysia who have poor access to healthcare. </p>		\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/dc-pic01-512x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" />											\n			<h2>About Our Portal</h2>		\n		<p>This is a multiracial and a multi-faith group of healthcare professionals ranging from doctors, dentists, nurses, pharmacists, physiotherapists, nutritionists, counsellors and medical/dental students. We are a universal group strictly without any political agenda, and are not associated with any particular organisation, foundation or religious society. Our sole purpose is to work with different groups from all over Malaysia, to provide quality medical screening and care for the needy and unfortunate irrespective of race, religion or nationality.</p>		\n										<img width=\"710\" height=\"533\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-300x225.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-768x576.jpg 768w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-1200x899.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-800x599.jpg 800w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08.jpg 1663w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" />											\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hypertension-867855_1920-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hypertension-867855_1920-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hypertension-867855_1920-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hypertension-867855_1920-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" />											\n		<p>Since August 2018, we have committed to medical service projects for adult &amp; children, with core scope of services pertaining to</p>\n<p>&nbsp;1) Outpatient clinic</p>\n<p>&nbsp;2) Non communicable diseases</p><p>&nbsp;3) Cardiac screening</p><p>&nbsp;4) Dermatology</p><p>&nbsp;5) Dental screening</p><p>&nbsp;6) Optometry and vision screening</p><p>&nbsp;7) Maternal &amp; child health.</p>		\n		<p>Our team of committed healthcare professionals will work together to form a structured medical camp with emphasis on patient health and general well-being.&nbsp;</p><p>The main emphasis is focused on health education and screening for early intervention to prevent complications<br></p>		\n										<img width=\"710\" height=\"373\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic07-1200x630.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic07-1200x630.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic07-600x315.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" />											\n		<p>In addition to the services provided, we try to actively look out for the very poor and destitute who are in need of medical/financial welfare, and sponsorship for the needy is provided from time to time.</p><p>Patients who have unresolved issues are followed up from time to time by liaison doctors who work around the vicinity, creating a continuation of care. If there are available volunteers, physiotherapy is offered on an ad-hoc basis, especially to the abandoned elderly who often visit due to chronic aches and pains.</p><p>Volunteers for this medical project come from diverse backgrounds all over Malaysia and Singapore, and they work hand in hand with the diligent volunteers from Sai Ananda Foundation. Everyone who joins in is reminded before every camp that compassion for suffering and love for everyone irrespective of race religion position or nationality are the only necessary ingredients to make this service project a success.</p><p> </p>		\n										<img width=\"710\" height=\"473\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-768x512.jpg 768w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-1200x799.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-800x533.jpg 800w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1.jpg 1871w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" />											\n										<img width=\"710\" height=\"473\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-768x512.jpg 768w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-1200x799.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-800x533.jpg 800w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1.jpg 1871w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" />											\n										<img width=\"710\" height=\"473\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-300x200.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-768x512.jpg 768w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-1200x799.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-800x533.jpg 800w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16.jpg 1871w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px\" />											\n			<h2>The reason of our doing</h2>		\n		<p>One of the challenges we faced during each medical camp is inadequate medical and dental volunteers. This is the reason why we are linking up healthcare professionals all around Malaysia and the Asia Pacific region through this universal portal called Doctors Connect. We also aim to work with other countries to expand our pool of resources, so that we can do much more for the society collectively.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>In the coming months, we will be launching a Doctors Connect website, which will showcase our work through different groups all over Asia Pacific region and more importantly, share stories of love and transformation by volunteers. We hope that with this move, more and more people will be inspired to take up volunteer work for the betterment of society and the world.&nbsp;</p><p>The other reason for forming this portal is to assure all healthcare professionals who have volunteered here, that the medical camps we host will be of a certain standard. Medical camps here are mainly organised by doctors, as we aim to use our experience to provide the maximal benefit to the poor and needy patients.</p><p>We hope to increase our volunteers base in Malaysia by 50% through this new portal and hope to conduct one medical camp per month from the current once in two or three months.</p><p>For doctors, a well-run medical camp is like dining at a good restaurant, chances to come back are high if the food is good. Therefore, all our events are carefully planned in advance by our medical and non-medical think-tank team, to ensure we select the right area that is genuinely in need of help, and deliver what is appropriately needed to them. In the end, it should be a win-win situation for everyone, as our patients and our volunteers should feel happy and good after every camp. </p><p>If we can work together despite all our differences, to reach out and help the poor and needy, then this effort to unite people through Doctors Connect will truly be a worthwhile cause. And in return, we should feel good after every event and eventually transform to become better individuals in time to come, which is the ultimate objective of these events. </p>		\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic15-1-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic15-1-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic15-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic15-1-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" />											\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/doctor-512x512.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/doctor-512x512.png 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/doctor-150x150.png 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/doctor-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" />											\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic18-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic18-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic18-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic18-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" />											\n			<h2>STATISTICS</h2>		\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village.png 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village-300x300.png 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village-150x150.png 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" />											\n		<p><strong>5</strong><strong> REGULAR VILLAGES ADOPTED </strong></p>		\n										<img width=\"256\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/256-256-2c37b3b4773fe68693b364649ae82b0c-patient.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/256-256-2c37b3b4773fe68693b364649ae82b0c-patient.png 256w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/256-256-2c37b3b4773fe68693b364649ae82b0c-patient-150x150.png 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/256-256-2c37b3b4773fe68693b364649ae82b0c-patient-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\" />											\n		<p><strong>497</strong> <strong>PATIENTS SEEN TILL DATE WITH REGULAR FOLLOW UP CAMPS </strong></p>		\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital.png 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital-300x300.png 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital-150x150.png 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" />											\n		<p><strong>100-120 </strong><strong> PATIENTS SCREENED PER MEDICAL CAMP </strong></p>		\n										<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512.png 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512-300x300.png 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512-150x150.png 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" />											\n		<p><strong>6</strong><strong> SPECIALITIES OFFERED </strong></p>		\n			<h2>Our Location</h2>		\n			<iframe frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Klang%20Valley%20&amp;t=m&amp;z=10&amp;output=embed&amp;iwloc=near\" aria-label=\"Klang Valley \"></iframe>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"310\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/night.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/night.png 620w, http://d