onnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic01-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"Eye examination\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic07-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"Regular health check\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic03-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"Regular health check-up\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic18-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"Child health screening\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic04-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"Complete medicine stocks\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic12-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"Fully fledged Pharmacy\" /></figure>			\n						Previous\n						Next\n			<h2>We pledged ourselves to be fully committed to the community, we are doing so by always providing the best service for the people through our programs, medical staff, and medical supplies.</h2>		\n			<h2>Images of our service</h2>		\n			<figure><img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic13-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic13-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic13-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic13-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></figure><h3>Computerized eye examination</h3><p>We always bring our Auto-refractometer with us so that our patient can get the best result for eye examination</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></figure><h3>Dental examination<br></h3><p><br>Our experienced dentist are also prepared for dental examination for people that needing it</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic05-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic05-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic05-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic05-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></figure><h3>Full eye examination</h3><p>Our optometrists are always prepared to check the condition of our patients<br></p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic10-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic10-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic10-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic10-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></figure><h3>Fully fledged Pharmacy with high quality specialist medication </h3><p>Our medication supplies are restock regulary and prepared for variety of illness</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic01-1-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic01-1-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic01-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic01-1-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></figure><h3>Mobile clinic<br></h3><p>We have an armada of mobile clinic to ease our sole aim is in creating access for quality healthcare to remote inaccessible and poor socio-economic areas </p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic12-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic12-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic12-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic12-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></figure><h3>Fully fledged pharmacist</h3><p><br>Our experienced pharmacist are ready to prepare our patients with the best medication for them</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/portable-ultra-sound-system-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/portable-ultra-sound-system-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/portable-ultra-sound-system-300x300.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/portable-ultra-sound-system-150x150.jpg 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/portable-ultra-sound-system-200x200.jpg 200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/portable-ultra-sound-system.jpg 614w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></figure><h3>Fully equipped general clinic with vitals counter and ECG services</h3><p>We are equipped with the state of the art technology in aiding our patient.<br></p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic19-512x512.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic19-512x512.jpg 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic19-150x15