 organisation, foundation or religious society. Our sole purpose is to work with different groups from all over Malaysia, to provide quality medical screening and care for the needy and unfortunate irrespective of race, religion or nationality.\n\n<img width=\"768\" height=\"576\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-768x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-768x576.jpg 768w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-300x225.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-1200x899.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08-800x599.jpg 800w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Dengkil-pic08.jpg 1663w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\">\n<img width=\"960\" height=\"660\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/heart-4248636_1920-1024x704.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/heart-4248636_1920-1024x704.jpg 1024w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/heart-4248636_1920-300x206.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/heart-4248636_1920-768x528.jpg 768w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/heart-4248636_1920-1536x1056.jpg 1536w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/heart-4248636_1920-1200x825.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/heart-4248636_1920-800x550.jpg 800w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/heart-4248636_1920.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\">\n\nSince August 2018, we have committed to medical service projects for adult &amp; children, with core scope of services pertaining to\n\n&nbsp;1) Outpatient clinic\n\n&nbsp;2) Non communicable diseases\n\n&nbsp;3) Cardiac screening\n\n&nbsp;4) Dermatology\n\n&nbsp;5) Dental screening\n\n&nbsp;6) Optometry and vision screening\n\n&nbsp;7) Maternal &amp; child health.\n\nOur team of committed healthcare professionals will work together to form a structured medical camp with emphasis on patient health and general well-being.&nbsp;\n\nThe main emphasis is focused on health education and screening for early intervention to prevent complications\n\n<img src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic07-1200x630.jpg\" title=\"Kalumpang-pic07\" alt=\"Kalumpang-pic07\">\n\nIn addition to the services provided, we try to actively look out for the very poor and destitute who are in need of medical/financial welfare, and sponsorship for the needy is provided from time to time.\n\nPatients who have unresolved issues are followed up from time to time by liaison doctors who work around the vicinity, creating a continuation of care. If there are available volunteers, physiotherapy is offered on an ad-hoc basis, especially to the abandoned elderly who often visit due to chronic aches and pains.\n\nVolunteers for this medical project come from diverse backgrounds all over Malaysia and Singapore, and they work hand in hand with the diligent volunteers from Sai Ananda Foundation. Everyone who joins in is reminded before every camp that compassion for suffering and love for everyone irrespective of race religion position or nationality are the only necessary ingredients to make this service project a success.\n\n<img width=\"960\" height=\"639\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-768x512.jpg 768w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-1200x799.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1-800x533.jpg 800w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic12-1.jpg 1871w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\">\n<img width=\"960\" height=\"639\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-768x512.jpg 768w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-1200x799.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1-800x533.jpg 800w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic10-1.jpg 1871w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\">\n<img width=\"960\" height=\"639\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-1024x682.jpg 1024w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-300x200.jpg 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-768x512.jpg 768w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-1200x799.jpg 1200w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16-800x533.jpg 800w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kalumpang-pic16.jpg 1871w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\">\n<h2>The reason of our doing</h2>\nOne of the challenges we faced during each medical camp is inadequate medical and dental volunteers. This is the reason why we are linking up healthcare professionals all around Malaysia and the Asia Pacific region through this universal portal called Doctors Connect. We also aim to work with other countries to expand our pool of resources, so that we can do much more for the society collectively.\n\nIn the coming months, we will be launching a Doctors Connect website, which will showcase our work through different groups all over Asia Pacific region and more importantly, share stories of love and transformation by volunteers. We hope that with this move, more and more people will be inspired to take up volunteer work for the betterment of society and the world.&nbsp;\n\nThe other reason for forming this portal is to assure all healthcare professionals who have volunteered here, that the medical camps we host will be of a certain standard. Medical camps here are mainly organised by doctors, as we aim to use our experience to provide the maximal benefit to the poor and needy patients.\n\nWe hope to increase our volunteers base in Malaysia by 50% through this new portal and hope to conduct one medical camp per month from the current once in two or three months.\n\nFor doctors, a well-run medical camp is like dining at a good restaurant, chances to come back are high if the food is good. Therefore, all our events are carefully planned in advance by our medical and non-medical think-tank team, to ensure we select the right area that is genuinely in need of help, and deliver what is appropriately needed to them. In the end, it should be a win-win situation for everyone, as our patients and our volunteers should feel happy and good after every camp.&nbsp;\n\nIf we can work together despite all our differences, to reach out and help the poor and needy, then this effort to unite people through Doctors Connect will truly be a worthwhile cause. And in return, we should feel good after every event and eventually transform to become better individuals in time to come, which is the ultimate objective of these events.&nbsp;\n\n<img src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic15-1-512x512.jpg\" title=\"Kerling-pic15\" alt=\"Kerling-pic15\">\n<img src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/dc-pic01-512x400.jpg\" title=\"dc-pic01\" alt=\"dc-pic01\">\n<img src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Kerling-pic18-512x512.jpg\" title=\"Kerling-pic18\" alt=\"Child health screening\">\n<h2>STATISTICS</h2>\n<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village.png 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village-300x300.png 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village-150x150.png 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/village-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\">\n\n<strong>5</strong><strong> REGULAR VILLAGES ADOPTED </strong>\n\n<img width=\"256\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/256-256-2c37b3b4773fe68693b364649ae82b0c-patient.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/256-256-2c37b3b4773fe68693b364649ae82b0c-patient.png 256w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/256-256-2c37b3b4773fe68693b364649ae82b0c-patient-150x150.png 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/256-256-2c37b3b4773fe68693b364649ae82b0c-patient-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 256px) 100vw, 256px\">\n\n<strong>497</strong> <strong>PATIENTS SEEN TILL DATE WITH REGULAR FOLLOW UP CAMPS </strong>\n\n<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital.png 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital-300x300.png 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital-150x150.png 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/hospital-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\">\n\n<strong>100-120 </strong><strong>&nbsp;PATIENTS SCREENED PER MEDICAL CAMP </strong>\n\n<img width=\"512\" height=\"512\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512.png 512w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512-300x300.png 300w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512-150x150.png 150w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/icon_medical-29-512-200x200.png 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\">\n\n<strong>6</strong><strong> SPECIALITIES OFFERED </strong>\n\n<img width=\"620\" height=\"310\" src=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/night.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/night.png 620w, http://doctorsconnect.test/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/night-300x150.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\">','About Doctors Connect Malaysia','','inherit','closed','closed','','6-revision-v1','','','2020-01-24 15:41:12','2020-01-24 15:41:12','',6,'http://doctorsconnect.test/?p=293',0,'revision','',0),(294,5,'2020-01-24 15:52:34','2020-01-24 15:52:34','{\n    \"custom_css[Nebula-master]\": {\n        \"value\": \"#primary-nav ul a{\\n\\tfont-size: 30px;\\n  color: #ffffff;\\n  text-shadow: -1px -1px 0 #000, 1px -1px 0 #000, -1px 1px 0 #000, 1px 1px 0 #000;\\n}\\n#bigheadingcon {\\n\\tbackground-image:url(\\\"http://getwallpapers.com/wallpaper/full/b/e/1/301842.jpg\\\");\\n\\t\\n\\t\\n}\\n.entry-title{\\n\\ttext-shadow: -2px -2px 0 #000, 2